description: BOCA CHICA, Texas - SpaceX's Starship rocket, designed to eventually send astronauts to the moon and beyond, completed nearly an entire test flight on its third try on Thursday, making it farther than before through a cruise in low orbit but was destroyed during atmospheric re-entry, the company said. REUTERS Read more at straitstimes.com.
title: Spacex confirms loss of starship at end of third test flight
title_page: Spacex confirms loss of starship at end of third test flight | The Straits Times
maintext: BOCA CHICA, Texas - SpaceX's Starship rocket, designed to eventually send astronauts to the moon and beyond, completed nearly an entire test flight on its third try on Thursday, making it farther than before through a cruise in low orbit but was destroyed during atmospheric re-entry, the company said.
